      "content": "that makes sense. can you get more specific about the \"classic\" look? like, if i'm giving advice to someone traveling to places like Singapore, Lagos, or London, what should the baseline \"professional\" outfit look like for a high-end business meeting? i want to make sure they don't look out of place.",
